<COREF ID="38" TYPE="IDENT">Global allocation funds</COREF> take the asset - allocation concept one step further by <COREF ID="39" TYPE="IDENT">investing</COREF> at least 25 % of <COREF ID="38" TYPE="IDENT">their</COREF> portfolios outside the U.S. .
