`` That 's <COREF ID="22" TYPE="IDENT">the problem with trying to hedge too much</COREF> , '' said <COREF ID="18" TYPE="IDENT">Mr. Brouwer</COREF> .
`` You <COREF ID="22" TYPE="IDENT">do</COREF> n't make any real money . ''
